        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item reveal">
        <div class="tip-icon">🔉</div>
        <div class="tip-content">
          <h4>渐进式叫我</h4>
          <p>不要突然大声叫。可以先小声说一句，等我回应了，再正常音量说话。就像"嘿…"→ 等我看你 → 再说"baby"。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item reveal">
        <div class="tip-icon">⏱️</div>
